getOrders(address,uint256,uint8,uint8,ui.details: Retrieves a list of orders that match the specified criteria.

params.collection: The address of the NFT collection.
params.count: The maximum number of orders to retrieve.
params.firstOrderKey: The key of the first order to retrieve.
params.price: The maximum price of the orders to retrieve.
params.saleKind: The type of sale (fixed price or auction).
params.side: The side of the orders to retrieve (buy or sell).

returns.nextOrderKey: The key of the next order to retrieve.
returns.resultOrders: An array of orders that match the specified criteria.
